      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Each test contains multiple test cases. The first line contains the number of test cases t (1≤t≤100). The description of the test cases \nfollows.\n\nThe first line of each test case contains two integers p and q (1≤p,q≤108).",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Each test contains multiple test cases. The first line contains the number of test cases t (1≤t≤100). The description of the test cases \nfollows.\n\nThe first line of each test case contains two integers p and q (1≤p,q≤108).",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yt7uRTj7yyb2WbvdSYNbM",
      "type": "text",
